- Yeah?

636
01:00:12,200 --> 01:00:15,170
Won is coming home after his scheduled flight, right?

637
01:00:15,170 --> 01:00:16,530
He's not answering his phone.

638
01:00:16,530 --> 01:00:19,470
He came home, and then he went back to the airport.

639
01:00:19,470 --> 01:00:21,170
Oh yeah, you still haven't gone to Paris?

640
01:00:21,170 --> 01:00:24,300
I pushed it back because of work.

641
