Ha Na, what should Won do?

643
01:00:31,780 --> 01:00:33,720
Why?

644
01:00:36,310 --> 01:00:41,410
Won applied to be in charge of the service training program in Paris because of you.

645
01:00:41,410 --> 01:00:45,600
He said he wanted to be there before you, so he's leaving today.

646
01:00:52,080 --> 01:00:57,420
♬ I couldn't say no ♬

647
01:00:58,400 --> 01:01:02,000
♬ The more you ask the more I love ♬

648
01:01:02,720 --> 01:01:05,640
Why isn't he picking up?
♬ Even without any excuse ♬

649
01:01:05,640 --> 01:01:10,020
♬ Even without any excuse ♬

